title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 31 2022

description:
Author and analyst Gordon Chang joins C&B to discuss the Shanghai lockdown, China's role in the Ukraine war, North Korea, and China's population decline. C&B analyze Biden's energy speech. Buck Sexton vs. viral Jeopardy sports questions.
